videos.headline: Perkins burns the VA Tech defense for 39-yard TD
videos.description: Bryce Perkins fakes the handoff and scoots 39 yards down the field, evading defenders to score a Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perkins burns the VA Tech defense for 39-yard TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Perkins takes off for 67-yard TD
videos.description: Bryce Perkins scores his second rushing touchdown of the game for Virginia as he blazes 67 yards through the Virginia Tech defense to reach the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perkins takes off for 67-yard TD) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tempers flare between Virginia and VA Tech in the 2nd quarter
videos.description: Penalties are called on both teams as Hasise Dubois is driven out of bounds all the way to the brick wall, causing an altercation after the play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tempers flare between Virginia and VA Tech in the 2nd quarter) 2019/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hooker keeps it himself for a 34-yard TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker fakes the handoff and takes off for a 34-yard touchdown to tie Virginia Tech's game with Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hooker keeps it himself for a 34-yard TD) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: VA Tech takes its 1st lead of the game
videos.description: Deshawn McClease takes the handoff and reaches the end zone from the one-yard line to give Virginia Tech a 20-13 lead over Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VA Tech takes its 1st lead of the game) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Perkins connects with Kemp for 25-yard TD
videos.description: Virginia ties the game at 20-20 as Bryce Perkins completes a pass to Billy Kemp IV, who evades a defender and leaps into the end zone to score a 25-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Perkins connects with Kemp for 25-yard TD) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: VA Tech retakes the lead on Turner's 61-yard TD
videos.description: Hendon Hooker completes a pass to a heavily covered Tre Turner, who makes his way into the end zone to score a 61-yard touchdown, giving Virginia Tech a 27-20 lead over Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (VA Tech retakes the lead on Turner's 61-yard TD) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Virginia ties it up on Taulapapa's short TD run
videos.description: Wayne Taulapapa takes the handoff and runs two yards into the end zone to score and tie the game at 27-27 early in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Virginia ties it up on Taulapapa's short TD run) 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Virginia fans rush the field after defeating VA Tech
videos.description: Virginia fans and students rush the field after the last play of the game as Virginia defeats Virginia Tech for the first time in 15 meetings.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Virginia fans rush the field after defeating VA Tech) 2019/11/29
